      **                                    171 180 DBPGM
      **                                    181 1830DBASE
      *
     ISDBANK    E DSSDBANKPD
      *
     IDSFDY     E DSDSFDY
      *
      ** Data Area giving Installation Control Details
      *
     IPSDS       SDS
