      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  XMSLAC - Read GLSLACPD and update account details            *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: Main Processing                                   *
      *                                                               *
      *  Calls:     XSIV01, XMACCN                                    *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           XMSLAC    BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         CTR     60
      *
     C           *LOVAL    SETLLGLSLACL8
     C                     READ GLSLACL8                 90
      *
     C           *IN90     DOWEQ'0'
     C                     MOVE SLFCNU    KCNUM
     C                     MOVE SLCCY     KCCY
     C                     MOVE SLFACO    KACOD
     C                     MOVE SLFACS    KACSQ
     C                     MOVE SLFBRC    KBRCA
      *
     C           KACCN     CHAINACCNTL0              2122
      *
     C           *IN21     IFEQ *ON
     C           *IN22     OREQ *ON
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     MOVEL'005'     DBASE
     C                     MOVEL'ACCNTL0 'DBFILE
     C                     OUT  LDA
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ELSE
      *
     C           ATYP      IFEQ 'R'
     C           LTAC      ANDEQ0
      *
     C           PRQCD     IFEQ 'C'
     C                     MOVE 'D'       DDIS
     C                     MOVE 'D'       CDIS
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           PRQCD     IFEQ 'W'
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   DDIS
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   CDIS
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     UPDATACCNTABF
      *
     C           CTR       ADD  1         CTR
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     READ GLSLACL8                 90
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE 'C'       PRTCD
     C                     MOVE CTR       PUCTR
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRINIT - Initialise and define fields                        *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: Main Processing                                   *
      *                                                               *
      *  Calls:     None                                              *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRINIT    BEGSR
      *
      ** Set up copyright parameter
      *
     C                     MOVEACPY@      CPY2@  80
      *
      ** Retrieve Run Date.
      *
     C                     CALL 'AOBANKR0'             9090
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   @RTCD   7
     C                     PARM '*FIRST ' @OPTN   7
     C           SDBANK    PARM SDBANK    DSFDY
      *
      ** If return with an error (LR seton in called program) then
      ** process for database error.
      *
     C           *IN90     IFEQ '1'
     C********** @RTCD     OREQ '*ERROR*'                                                   BUG27769
     C           @RTCD     ORNE *BLANKS                                                     BUG27769
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     MOVEL'AOBANKR0'DBFILE
     C                     MOVEL'*FIRST'  DBKEY
     C                     Z-ADD007       DBASE
     C                     OUT  LDA
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE 'F'       PRTCD
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  @DEFN - Definition Routine (Not Called)                      *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: None                                              *
      *                                                               *
      *  Calls:     None                                              *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           @DEFN     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PRTCD   1
     C                     PARM           PRQCD   1
     C                     PARM           PUCTR   6
      *
     C           *NAMVAR   DEFN           LDA
      *
     C           *LIKE     DEFN CNUM      KCNUM
     C           *LIKE     DEFN CCY       KCCY
     C           *LIKE     DEFN ACOD      KACOD
     C           *LIKE     DEFN ACSQ      KACSQ
     C           *LIKE     DEFN BRCA      KBRCA
      *
     C           KACCN     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           KCNUM
     C                     KFLD           KCCY
     C                     KFLD           KACOD
     C                     KFLD           KACSQ
     C                     KFLD           KBRCA
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      * *PSSR  - Program exception error routine                      *
      *          Called automatically if a program error occurs,      *
      *          or directly by the program code using EXSR.          *
      *          This subroutine DUMPs the program just once.         *
      *                                                               *
      * Called by: (**calling routines**)                             *
      *                                                               *
      * Calls: None                                                   *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           *PSSR     BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVE 'F'       PRTCD
     C           @RUN      IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       @RUN    1
     C                     DUMP
     C                     END
      *
     C                     ROLBK
     C                     SETON                     U7U8LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
